// =================================================================
// Program: DeliveryPartner.partner_comments_zh - the data in
//          English of the partner comments carousel of the delivery
//          partner web page.
// Author : Bill Huang
// Date   : Oct 19 - Dec 18, 2019
// =================================================================
const PartnerComments = [{
  "id": "1",
  "imgSrc": "/imgs/delivery/delivery-partner-comment-zenq.jpg",
  "slideTitle": "ZenQ",
  "slideCaption": "As a restaurant brand with multiple branches in Toronto, we have a deep relationship with Fantuan. We have witnessed Fantuan’s prosperity since they settled in Toronto, and today, Fantuan is our first choice for food delivery platforms. Fantuan always has unique ideas in food delivery service, which is why we decided to exclusively partner with them. By supporting this platform, we’re also supporting a new dining experience, different from dine-in. Another reason for supporting Fantuan is so new customers see us on their platform. Thank you Fantuan!"
}, {
  "id": "2",
  "imgSrc": "/imgs/delivery/delivery-partner-comment-meet.jpg",
  "slideTitle": "Meet You Leisure",
  "slideCaption": "A few years ago, we put forward the idea of ​​exclusive cooperation with Fantuan Delivery. At that time, we had cooperated with almost all delivery platforms on the market, but Fantuan had impeccable professionalism and specifications. The delivery uniforms and punctuality, professional order software and timely customer service helps us feel that we are not only a cooperation business, but also a valued partner of Fantuan. They have helped us a lot - we trust and cherish Fantuan!"
}, {
  "id": "3",
  "imgSrc": "/imgs/delivery/delivery-partner-comment-weixiaochu.jpg",
  "slideTitle": "徽小厨",
  "slideCaption": "As soon as we opened the store, we chose Fantuan Delivery. Its sincerity and being a steadily rising development trend for businesses attracted us to it since the beginning. Since joining their platform, Fantuan has brought us a large number of deliveries and new customers using various promotions and advertisements. I firmly believe that when I choose Fantuan Delivery, I choose the best!"
}, {
  "id": "4",
  "imgSrc": "/imgs/delivery/delivery-partner-comment-dapaimaocai.jpg",
  "slideTitle": "",
  "slideCaption": "I personally always recommend Fantuan. Although there are a lot of Chinese food delivery platforms in Toronto, Fantuan has always been very good, and their delivery staff come quickly. When we first opened the store, Fantuan also tried their best to help us with publicity, which had a good effects. Even when unexpected situations arise, Fantuan’s marketing staff will come negotiate with us first and strive to minimize the impact for not only customers, but also their partners. Fantuan has always been implementing their slogan: \"Life made easier.\" If I get the ability to open more stores in the future, I will continue to partner with Fantuan. Thank you."
}, {
  "id": "5",
  "imgSrc": "/imgs/delivery/delivery-partner-comment-zoe.jpg",
  "slideTitle": "Zoe Dessert & PresoTea",
  "slideCaption": "Fantuan has always been our friendly partner. Only fast delivery can maintain the taste and quality of food. Zoe Dessert & PresoTea always pays great attention to the guarantee of food quality, and Fantuan surely meets those expectations."
}, {
  "id": "6",
  "imgSrc": "/imgs/delivery/delivery-partner-comment-xianghunan.jpg",
  "slideTitle": "湘湖南",
  "slideCaption": "We did not hesitate much to cooperate with Fantuan Delivery when it expands to Montreal, as it is the largest Chinese delivery platform in Canada. Later relationship with them proved our correct choice by experiencing Fantuan's professional heat preservation facility, premium delivery service that demonstrates their care of the restaurant, the food quality, and customer experience."
}, {
  "id": "7",
  "imgSrc": "/imgs/delivery/delivery-partner-comment-baiyulan.jpg",
  "slideTitle": "BAIYULAN",
  "slideCaption": "After partnering with Fantuan, our restaurant has attracted more and more customers. They also helped us with marketing and promotion. I am very satisfied with their service."
}];
export default PartnerComments;

